OL,3,CMan and dog attacked by 'out of
OL,4,Ccontrol' cockapoo-terrier cross
OL,6,FPolice in Kent are trying to trace a
OL,7,Fdog which escaped its owner and
OL,8,Fattacked a man and his dog in
OL,9,FSheerness.
OL,11,FOfficers received reports that the
OL,12,Foffending dog, a cockapoo and border
OL,13,Fterrier cross, was running dangerously
OL,14,Fout of control on Scrapsgate Road in
OL,15,FMinster on Sea at around 5pm on
OL,16,FTuesday 24th March.
OL,18,FThe victim sustained multiple cuts to
OL,19,Fhis hands, while his dog suffered an
OL,20,Finjury to its neck which required
OL,21,Fstitches.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
