OL,3,CMan and dog attacked by 'out of
OL,4,Ccontrol' cockapoo-terrier cross
OL,6,FOfficers have carried out a number of
OL,7,Fenquiries since the incident to
OL,8,Fidentify the dog and its owner and are
OL,9,Fnow appealing to the public for
OL,10,Finformation.
